		<h1 class="static_page"> A Competitor's Investor is Your Enemy </h1>

		<blockquote>
		  <p>“VCs will tell your secrets to your competitors if they end up investing in them. It's not unheard of for VCs to meet you when they have no intention of funding you, just to pick your brain for a competitor.”</p>
		  <footer> <a href="http://www.paulgraham.com/venturecapital.html"> Paul Graham, Y Combinator </a> </footer>
		</blockquote>

